      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·010.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">六月.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>比物四驪，閑之維則。維此六月，既成我服。
我服既成，于三十里。王于出征，以佐天子。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Matched in strength were the four black steeds,
Well trained to observe every rule.
On this sixth month,
We completed our accountrements.
Our accountrements were completed,
And we marched thirty Li every day.
The king had ordered the expedition,
To help the son of Heaven.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-nanyoujiayu-010__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
