      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·010.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">六月.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>四牡脩廣，其大有顒。薄伐玁狁，以奏膚公。
有嚴有翼，共武之服。共武之服，以定王國。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The four steeds were long, and stout,
And large-headed.
We smote the Xian-yun,
And achieved great merit.
Severely strict and careful was our leader,
Discharging his military service, --
Discharging his military service,
And settling thereby the royal kingdom.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-nanyoujiayu-010__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
