      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·010.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">六月.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>戎車既安，如輊如軒。四牡既佶，既佶且閑。
薄伐玁狁，至于大原。文武吉甫，萬邦為憲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The war carriages were well made.
Nicely balanced, before and behind.
Their four steeds were strong,
Both strong and well trained.
We smote the Xian-yun,
As far as Tai-yuan.
For peace or for war fit is Ji-fu,
A pattern to all the States.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-nanyoujiayu-010__006__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
