      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·010.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">六月.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>吉甫燕喜，既多受祉。來歸自鎬，我行永久。
飲御諸友，炰鱉膾鯉。侯誰在矣？張仲孝友。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Ji-fu feasts and is glad;
Great happiness is his.
In returning from Hao,
Distant and long had been our march.
He entertains and feasts his friends,
With roast turtle and minced carp.
And who are there?
There is Zhang Zhong, the filial and brotherly.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
